you just say [ten one, ten two] et cetera.

35
00:03:11,640 --> 00:03:17,590
[Shí yī, shí èr]

36
00:03:17,630 --> 00:03:21,790
Let's see some more numbers.

37
00:03:22,040 --> 00:03:25,620
Read the list with me, please.

38
